Text: FW May BCAlberta Import and Export InterTie trans fer Forecast Cc PST Richey I dont believe this will be a problem Please allow a couple of days and we should be able to have an excel sheet up We will announce with a headline on our website Rob Baker Original Message From Thursby Murray Sent Friday June AM To Baker Rob Billinton Jeff Subject FW May BCAlberta Import and Export InterTie transfer Forecast Good morning guys Can you help Cooper out Thnaks Murray T Original Message From Richey Cooper mailtoCooper NRONcom mailtomailtoCooper NRONcom Sent Thursday June PM To mailto Subject May BCAlberta Import and Export InterTie transfer Forecast Recently you posted a May BCAlberta Import and Export InterTie transfer Forecast in a pdf format on your website Can I obtain a copy of this file in a text format csv or similar Thanks Cooper
